snippet.title: BATTLE HUNTERS coming soon to Switch and Steam
snippet.description:
A classic-style RPG adventure with unique tactical real-time combat, loads of heroes to discover, and a huge variety of monsters to battle! Coming soon to Nintendo Switch and Steam.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1393340/Battle_Hunters/
